      What's the latest Call of Duty?
      Several spin-off and handheld games were made by other developers. The most recent title, Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III, was released on November 10, 2023. The upcoming title, Call of Duty: Black Ops 6, is scheduled to be released on October 25, 2024.

      Call of Duty: Black Ops

      About

      Description

      Call of Duty: Mobile is a 2019 first-person shooter video game developed by TiMi Studio Group and published by Activision for Android and iOS. Released as a free-to-play title, it was one of the largest mobile game launches in history, generating over US$480 million with 270 million downloads within a year. Wikipedia
      Initial release date: 1 October 2019
      Developers: Activision, TiMi Studio Group, Tencent Games
      Awards: BAFTA Games Award for EE Mobile Game of the Year, The Game Award for Best Mobile Game
      Nominations: BAFTA Games Award for EE Mobile Game of the Year, The Game Award for Best Mobile Game
      Genres: Battle royale game, First-person shooter
      Platforms: Android, iOS
      Publishers: Activision, Level Infinite, VNG Game Publishing
